                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>In dem Meeserschen Hause<lb/> über der\n                                                  Brücke<lb/> am Neckar <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >Heidelberg</hi></placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>March 9<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1854</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Dear friend</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I am taking the opportunity<lb/> of writing a\n                                        little to you by a Gentleman<lb/> about to leave\n                                                  <placeName>Heidelberg</placeName> for\n                                                  <placeName>New York</placeName>. I<lb/> have not\n                                        your correct address here; I<lb/> therefore must trust to\n                                        his kindness in<lb/> sending it safely to you at\n                                                  <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.<lb/> When I\n                                        last heard from my dear family<lb/> one of my sisters wrote\n                                        to say that the “<hi rend=\"underline\">Occident</hi>”<lb/>\n                                        had been sent to me in\n                                                  <placeName>Baker<add>?</add></placeName> in which\n                                        they read<lb/> a <hi rend=\"underline\">beautiful</hi> notice\n                                        of my Poems from<lb/> your gifted mind, with some\n                                        pieces<lb/> transcribed. I assure you I appreciate<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">much</hi> your kindness also for\n                                        the<lb/> advertisement therein—my sisters have<lb/>\n                                        requested two more copies to be sent<lb/> for them &amp; I\n                                        am to receive <hi rend=\"underline\">my</hi><lb/> number in\n                                                  <date>May</date>, when <persName>Mr\n                                                  Simon's</persName><lb/> family are going to visit\n                                        us, en route</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3w08x281/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
